{"tid":2336714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"作為應屆DSE考生 我有啲嘢想講…","createTime":"2020-12-22T21:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T19:04:53.000Z","uid":326404,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c16a9879832378e8fafec2748d69c00070a79e1b","tid":2336714,"uid":326404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T21:13:20.000Z","msg":"我預咗又有人話鬥慘 你鍾意點諗就點諗<br />\n目前嚟睇 如果下年初疫情搞唔掂<br />\n最慘會係2022年考生<br />\n我哋起碼叫過咗一年高中生活<br />\n<br />\n諗番起兩年前<br />\n啱啱上高中終於可以去CB 個陣仲怕醜<br />\n唔敢搵囡囡影相<br />\n諗住下年脫毒之後再搵<br />\n結果 垃圾毅進仔鳩放TG 令學校因為安全取消所有活動 包括旅行 CB Sports Day<br />\n<br />\n原本想話一年啫 最多F.6再嚟<br />\n點知支那又整個肺炎 成年唔洗番學<br />\n毫無懸念 今年又係所有嘢都冇<br />\n最慘嘅係 依家Grad din都好大機會搞唔成<br />\nGrad din應該係一生人入面第二樣重要嘅宴會<br />\n除咗婚禮以外最期待嘅嘢 依家乜都冇<br />\n<br />\n我唔想有生之年 我個孫問我高中有咩玩<br />\n「你阿爺當年好好玩架 玩完半年香城online<br />\n之後又留係屋企打足成年半機唔洗番學」<br />\n點諗到F.4個次CB 會係成個中學生涯唯一一次<br />\n呢個仇我會記一世 支那狗仲有班毅進狗<br />\n<br />\n不過咁諗 起碼我哋都有一年嘅高中生活<br />\n下屆可能隨時一年都冇<br />\n<br />\n純粹凌晨訓唔著 突然好撚Sad想悔氣<br />\n聽日又要乖乖地繼續溫DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea2c72b79cd5e2c46c19b549c1afd736834c6ff","tid":2336714,"uid":79117,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T21:15:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cf573186b60560bfc451b4daa4bcf2a25ad9eba","tid":2336714,"uid":377811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ea2c72b79cd5e2c46c19b549c1afd736834c6ff","tid":2336714,"uid":79117,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T21:15:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T21:40:31.000Z","msg":"想當年我都要keep住做cdrom 等到入到u先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6fa0a53947a50aeafd8f5718d4ef06ce6f4d7b","tid":2336714,"uid":17761,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T21:45:29.000Z","msg":"Grad din唔洗睇得咁重 當年全級得兩班去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7be8b21461372a20f7236ea9df9735fa70e881a","tid":2336714,"uid":370010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T22:02:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a072395a26d56db4cc00e77e7935b7f3fb8d047","tid":2336714,"uid":116910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T22:17:31.000Z","msg":"理論上應該有疫苖就ok既<br />\n<br />\n利申讀左一個sem 一次學校都未翻過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc04550ba3d1e8c591324800b8af50ed00446ab","tid":2336714,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T00:50:00.000Z","msg":"有低能仔逐個comment留負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831a1b7207187401cf225950b717fb7e886ef158","tid":2336714,"uid":312893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"樓主我都係應屆考生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾武肺搞到我無撚咗3個遊學團嘅機會<br />\n講緊係3個都搭飛機<br />\n學校資助最少一半嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌而家乜柒都無<br />\n真係唔知高中三年有咩回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw樓主温成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b07f586576c3c800a06f15f89b8f4ab62554886","tid":2336714,"uid":346660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:04:53.000Z","msg":"Grad din 通常6月7月搞 仲有成半年喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時疫情仲唔完? 咁就大獲啦全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}